    "description": "Explore and face the dangers of the poolrooms in an immersive cooperative horror game. You play as a scientist whose mission is to explore the depths of the poolrooms for research purposes. You will soon realise that you have made a mistake and that there is no way out. Through escaping from various creatures you will have to find a way out of there.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/a51690d72236e81eb2533ef83a6cad39.poster.avif?t=1739205983\" width=612 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/a51690d72236e81eb2533ef83a6cad39.webm?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/a51690d72236e81eb2533ef83a6cad39.mp4?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Singleplayer &amp; Co-op Multiplayer<br><br>- Proximity Voice Chat<br><br>- Host and join lobbies<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b85625977f5a93f75791ac5088671be8.poster.avif?t=1739205983\" width=612 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b85625977f5a93f75791ac5088671be8.webm?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b85625977f5a93f75791ac5088671be8.mp4?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as a scientist whose goal is to explore the poolrooms. Finding a way back to reality will be your main goal.<br>As part of their ongoing research into human consciousness, the Neuro-Bio-Psychology Laboratory (NBP) has developed a revolutionary new machine. That teleports you into another dimesion called Backrooms. It is up to you how long you stay there...<br>With this technology, they can explore these dimensions in search for answers to this misterious dimension.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/94d2d1bdaba76457b363869bd68490c8.poster.avif?t=1739205983\" width=612 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/94d2d1bdaba76457b363869bd68490c8.webm?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/94d2d1bdaba76457b363869bd68490c8.mp4?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game is powered by Unreal Engine 5 and we have focused on getting the best graphics possible to give you more immersion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b3616464393d39334b67a79477508ee3.poster.avif?t=1739205983\" width=612 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b3616464393d39334b67a79477508ee3.webm?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216840/extras/b3616464393d39334b67a79477508ee3.mp4?t=1739205983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To make the levels more entertaining, you will have to complete a series of puzzles in order to continue. There are many different types of puzzles you will have to complete to continue your journe. The solution is not always obvious, but if you follow the trail of clues, then it should become clear what needs to happen next.",
